Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回想起来，自从那天以来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来过这里多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，在这个星球我思念的只有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那小小的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.55,0:00:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.55,0:00:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我和千濑的定情之处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在那天，从这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这个地方开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(阿修)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作会不会太慢了啊，千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是慢吞吞的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,个子又小，胆子也很小
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成绩也只有中下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有世界史好得莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.61,0:02:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这无法成为将来谋生的一技之长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她自己也很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:02:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的口头禅是”对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的座右铭是”想要变得更坚强”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么看都觉得是个没有用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天还是像以前一样搭公车上学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想跟我一起爬地狱坡是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我不久以前还是田径队的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为，我是你的女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交换日记?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然不喜欢吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁怂恿你做这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是明美他们吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我真的想多了解你一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，你们两个不快点就会迟到喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明美，早妄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又在欺负千濑吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有欺负她！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，要迟到了喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法，我就陪你写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的女朋友，千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五天前她向我表白要我跟她交往
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.86,0:05:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在依然犹豫不决
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交换日记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦，你就陪她写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正晚上也没有什么事情可以做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电视老是在重播不然就是放电影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说手机跟网路现在又不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我该写什么好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛，比如说你今天一整天做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是去了什么地方之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正到了暑假就不会一直在一起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了学校和家里之外我还有什么地方能去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然你就写你喜欢干濑什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是想跟她接吻想跟她嘿咻之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说这个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹，你跟由佳利上床了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,思，毕竟我们交往两个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然已经上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来听嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不说因为说了会被你们当笑柄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点点就好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，等等我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去捡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，修次在看你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，明美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向她挥挥手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然又会被明美臭骂喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,F-15
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近经常在飞耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是发生什么事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:07:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说东京和大阪那边挺危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有事的啦，反正跟我们无关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交换日记啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.61,0:07:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，你现在在做什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在当然是在看日记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我提起勇气向你告白真的是做对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在每天都过得好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想．．．千濑，你好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假就快要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.84,0:07:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么计画...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，你在睡觉吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我醒著啦，现在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟女生交往，原来这么麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，我们要先吃罗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要一直叫我阿修啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可以随便进去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:09:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会被骂吗?这是基地里面耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系，反正只是基地的边缘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前都可以自由进出的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他终於把交换日记还你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了，千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(还是算了吧 不过放学後陪我一下)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出所料 我可以了解修次的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放学後...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是指”嘿咻”吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，我们没迷路吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里半个人都没有耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得现在还太早...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後我想让你看看这个景色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉，我已经累了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这个人不适合谈恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，并不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得很累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道男女交往该做些什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼命的问明美还看了一堆漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试著去做好多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全无法像别人一样顺利的谈恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,归根究底都是你的错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我根本就没想要跟你交往
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是为了试试胆量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改变我软弱的个性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为明美知道我一直很崇拜你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就叫我向你表白想说失败也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道你竟然答应跟我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般都会答应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:11:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要答应我?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你这么可爱的女孩告白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家当然会答应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你向人家告白前人家根本没打算和女生交往
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从小时候就这样说话 这有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，你好可爱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜!你比较可爱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实，我真的很怕你...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要一直说对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交往至今我好像是第一次看到你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许男女交往就像这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还是男朋友和女朋友吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然顺序有点混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得有缘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後我们要不要试著去喜欢对方看看?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那...那么...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，你希望我对你做什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了，我做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们打算从这里开始我们的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:15:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心脏跳得好大声喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个乡下的小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有任何乐趣可言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对未来也是茫茫然的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们两人已经决定了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要继续相恋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以偶尔打电话给你吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 路上小心点，不要跌倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，咖啡卖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由佳利和阿竹在吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜，不要随便认定他们是在吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，我向你道歉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个伤怎么来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又在家里跌倒了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么，不要紧的，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的很粗心大意耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微小心一点喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟你是个女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，我们两个也会吵架吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该吵不起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你经常哼这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我们要代替那个最後突然说不来的千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪你来札幌大采购呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话，闭上你的嘴巴快选啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没女朋友还要来买服饰 只是更空虚而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要请我吃烤玉米喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猪头，你是观光客啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是玫瑰水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是爱与疗伤的宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好喔，我也要买给我女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们两个吵架还没和好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是地震
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，这个地震很强喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像越来越近了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，去外面看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要出去，阿淳 这时候乱跑很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊，避难训练时学过了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猪头，别在这里说风凉话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是哪里的战斗机?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我们国家的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:18:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底出了什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之往大道公园逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊，这里太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿淳，你看上面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是F-2，从三泽来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次，快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个钟楼才刚刚修好的说...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿律，快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，修次，阿律，阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么?到底是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹，喂，阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿竹，你不可以死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来救救他，来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.89,0:21:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体变成了这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回想起来 那时候我应该察觉到才对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.21,0:22:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我抱著千濑 她的心脏却没有心跳声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.29,0:22:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,#01 我们将继续相恋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.90,0:22:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心中有一道裂缝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.87,0:22:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以入眠的夜里 总不停的叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.81,0:23:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉 黎明已悄然到来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.53,0:23:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么想听见你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.43,0:23:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感受你的体温
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.54,0:23:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你的思念越来越强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.84,0:23:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泪水夺眶而出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.58,0:23:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 我心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我仍无法忘怀 你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然只因一句再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.83,0:23:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要结束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.34,0:23:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫人感到悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.65,0:24:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，你说你变成终极武器是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.65,0:24:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要上战场打仗一下?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.46,0:24:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还只是高中生耶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.42,0:24:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.69,0:24:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终兵器彼女 下一回【我正在成长】
